OL,4,CJustin Welby tells Church of England to
OL,5,Cstop using NDAs amid racism claims
OL,6, The Archbishop of Canterbury has said
OL,7, the Church of England should not use
OL,8, non-disclosure agreements, after BBC
OL,9, Panorama revealed they were being used
OL,10, to silence staff complaining of racism.
OL,12,FJustin Welby said he had not been aware
OL,13,Fconfidentiality agreements were being
OL,14,Fused to stop people speaking publicly.
OL,16,FHe told Times Radio the documentary was
OL,17,F"rightly shaming".
OL,19,FMr Welby added that he was "horrified"
OL,20,Fto hear the extent of racist abuse
OL,21,Fwithin the Church.
